REQUIREMENTS
	-php 5.0+
	-mod_rewrite enabled
	-htaccess enabled
	-pdo enabled
	-hybridauth (optional) 
	-htmlpurifier (optional)

HYBRIDAUTH INTEGRATION
	-Add the fllowing line to index.php before line "Hybrid_Endpoint::process();"
	-require_once( '(path/to/project)/settings.php' );
	-require_once( BP_ROOT. "auth/session.php" );
